Version 1.1
===========
* Updated with GSOC contributions, thanks (and authorship) go to Andrea Storey.
* Added unit tests.
* Added functionality to calculate the banded and tapered estimate from McMurry and Politis (2010)
* Moved the target and lambda values (crucial in estimation) to the argument list with the previous values as defaults. This gives the user more control if wanted.
* Updated documentation.
* Added a vignette.

